{"title":"基于hexo博客系统的博客搭建流程","uid":"cf97b9a7f03f24963965d94ee552b26e","slug":"基于hexo博客系统的博客搭建流程","date":"2019-10-31T09:34:02.000Z","updated":"2019-10-31T09:35:07.550Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/基于hexo博客系统的博客搭建流程.json","keywords":"SeiyuYuri","cover":[],"content":"<p>应某位巨佬的委托，介绍一下基于hexo博客系统的博客搭建流程</p>\n<p>步骤有少许繁琐，请多多谅解。</p>\n<p>在这篇文章中，你会：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>下载并安装 “Git分布式版本控制系统”,以及针对博客的基础操作</strong></li>\n<li><strong>下载并安装 &quot;Nodejs&quot;以搭建运行环境</strong></li>\n<li><strong>下载并安装 &quot;hexo系统&quot;开始你的博客之旅!!</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p>1.下载  <a href=\"https://git-scm.com/\">Git</a><br>\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/SeiyuYuri/Picture/raw/master/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%93/Git.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>然后请安装(next就对了)</p>\n<p>你的程序列表之中应该出现了Git Bash,这是我们之后要用到的.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>2.下载<a href=\"https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/node/v12.13.0/\">Nodejs</a><br>\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/SeiyuYuri/Picture/raw/master/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%93/nodejs%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2.jpg\" alt=\"请自行根据系统选择\"></p>\n<p>然后请安装(同样next就对了)</p>\n<p>这是运行环境,不会直接使用.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>3.安装hexo系统</p>\n<p>前期准备:</p>\n<p>请准备好一个文件夹,以存储hexo相关文件.下文中的指令若未特别说明将默认在此目录下进行.(默认:  D://hexo  )</p>\n<p>3.1. 打开Git Bash,直接输入安装指令 (注:显示 <strong>$</strong> 即可输入指令.)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>电脑将自动下载hexo文件至nodejs文件库.</p>\n<p>3.2.将hexo安装至指定文件夹(之前准备的文件夹)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd D://hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>进入文件夹</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装hexo相关文件</p>\n<p>hexo会自动下载一些文件到这个目录，包括node_modules，这里有所有已安装插件</p>\n<p>##到此处,hexo系统已经搭建完成.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>4.hexo基本命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g        生成文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo s        开启hexo服务器(可进入http://localhost:4000查看博客效果)</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d        上传文件至指定库</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo clean    清理已生成文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo new post 生成新文章至source文件夹的_posts文件夹</span><br><span class=\"line\">&amp;&amp;            可用于指令之间，有空格的作用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<p>5.更改博客主题</p>\n<p>由于文章开头根据不同的博客主题会有不同种类,故最好先确定博客主题在进行写作.<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\">hexo博客主题</a></p>\n<p>请根据具体选择的博客主题进行配置.(一般博客说明目录将显示在其GitHub项目之下)</p>\n<p>更多hexo系统相关请参阅<a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">hexo官网</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://116.62.235.157/\">Alocpur OJ</a>用户可申请将生成文件上传至服务器.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>6.markdown基本语法</p>\n<p>请参阅<a href=\"http://118.31.13.93:20199/2019/10/22/markdown\">markdown语法</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"应某位巨佬的委托，介绍一下基于hexo博客系统的博客搭建流程 步骤有少许繁琐，请多多谅解。 在这篇文章中，你会： 下载并安装 “Git分布式版本控制系统”,以及...","permalink":"/post/基于hexo博客系统的博客搭建流程","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":956,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"blog","slug":"blog","count":2,"path":"api/categories/blog.json"},{"name":"hexo","slug":"blog/hexo","count":2,"path":"api/categories/blog/hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"blog","slug":"blog","count":2,"path":"api/tags/blog.json"},{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twit